        <p>This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which MOVTIC collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users (each, a 'User') of the www.MOVTIC.com website and MOVTIC app ('Site/App') (“Data”). This privacy policy applies to the Site/App and all products and services offered by MOVTIC (the “Service”). We use your Data to provide and improve the Service. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>
